# BMO Career x AI - Claude Rules & Context

## Project Overview

This is the **BMO Careers Website Redesign** project - a static HTML/CSS site with a sophisticated design-to-code workflow using Figma, FigJam, and GitHub Pages deployment.

**Live Site:** https://devjainshourya-alt.github.io/BMO-Careers/
**GitHub Repo:** https://github.com/devjainshourya-alt/BMO-Careers

### Tech Stack
- **Frontend:** HTML5, CSS3 (vanilla, no framework)
- **Font:** Heebo (Google Fonts)
- **Deployment:** GitHub Pages (auto-deploy from `main` branch)
