## Key Design System Elements

### Typography (Heebo)
- Headings: 600-700 weight
- Body: 400-500 weight
- Hero title: Large, bold
- Section headers: Medium weight
- Job cards: Mix of weights for hierarchy

### Color Palette
- **Primary Blue:** BMO brand blue (links, CTAs, accents)
- **White/Light Gray:** Backgrounds, cards
- **Dark Gray/Black:** Text, headings
- **Accent Colors:** Category tags, highlights

### Component Patterns
- **Job Cards:** Category tag + title + meta + CTA link
- **Career Cards:** Light variant (white bg) and Blue variant (blue bg)
- **Article Cards:** Image + date + title + link
- **Hero Section:** Full-bleed background + centered content + search bar
- **Navigation:** Dual-level (top locale bar + main nav), responsive hamburger
- **Footer:** Multi-column links + social icons + legal links

### Spacing Scale
Extracted from Figma, documented in `DESIGN_ANNOTATIONS.md`:
- Common gaps: 8px, 12px, 16px, 20px, 24px, 28px, 32px, 40px
- Section padding: 40px (desktop), 20px (tablet), 16px (mobile)
- Card padding: 28px (desktop/tablet), 16px (mobile)

